ZH: 这个教室有30个座位。
EN: This classroom has 30 seats.

ZH: 请坐到你的座位上。
EN: Please sit in your assigned seat.

ZH: 这个汽车上有5个座位。
EN: There are 5 seats in this car.

ZH: 我这个星期坐了很多小时的座位。
EN: I have spent many hours sitting in seats this week.

ZH: 请占好你的座位。
EN: Please take your seat.

ZH: 教室里的座位已经全部满了。
EN: All the seats in the classroom are full.

ZH: 这个公交车上有很多空座位。
EN: There are many empty seats on this bus.

ZH: 父母坐在前排座位上，孩子们坐在后面。
EN: The parents sit in the front seats, and the children sit in the back.

ZH: 我喜欢坐在窗边的座位上。
EN: I like to sit in the seat by the window.

ZH: 这是我们的固定座位。
EN: This is our assigned seat.

ZH: 学校的礼堂里摆满了座位。
EN: The auditorium at school is filled with seats.

ZH: 请不要随意选择座位。
EN: Please do not choose seats randomly.

ZH: 我们每个人都有自己的座位号码。
EN: Each of us has our own seat number.

ZH: 请把椅子放回原来的座位上。
EN: Please put the chair back in its original seat.

ZH: 这辆巴士坐满了座位。
EN: The bus is full of seats.

ZH: 我们可以在座位上留下我们的衣物。
EN: We can leave our belongings on the seats.

ZH: 警察示意我坐在他的座位上。
EN: The police officer gestured for me to sit in his seat.

ZH: 我的座位是在第十排。
EN: My seat is in the tenth row.

ZH: 请注意您周围的座位。
EN: Please pay attention to the seats around you.
